{"tid":2192205,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新巴職工會：被捕司機仍被扣查　有司機擬自發按章工作","createTime":"2020-09-07T03:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T04:51:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5d2ff13ea4101f5775d9f70adeecd14f101e13b","tid":2192205,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:33:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548247-20200907.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548247-20200907.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpxVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=c47b6562\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548247-20200907.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5a0aa341\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548247-20200907.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n有網民昨日發起九龍區遊行，期間警方在彌敦道近永星里登上一輛巴士截查，司機隨後被警方帶走。新巴職工會說，警方指司機涉嫌危險駕駛，要扣留48小時，但至今仍未落案，工會仍未接觸到這名司機。<br />\n<br />\n新巴職工會理事長林錦標在一個電台目表示，事後已請區議員及律師協助，目前公司要盡快取出巴士內的錄影和錄音器材以及黑盒，以解當時情況及巴士的車速等資料。<br />\n<br />\n林錦標說，有其他司機認為警方的處理手法不合理，說司機見到路上多人都不會加速駕駛，亦可能會因應對方有危險而響號示意。他又說，工會知道有司機計劃自發按章工作。"},{"pid":"39aa33afd1f101ef9d488c06a32418ec62804bd9","tid":2192205,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:46:18.000Z","msg":"班popo真係乜都政治化"},{"pid":"6742d83ccdea605be08cd19f3956f8aedfd9c340","tid":2192205,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"39aa33afd1f101ef9d488c06a32418ec62804bd9","tid":2192205,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:46:18.000Z","msg":"班popo真係乜都政治化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:59:42.000Z","msg":"香港我話事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7067cf022372677026ca0135452ac6cb7ce212a2","tid":2192205,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:51:02.000Z","msg":"轉行